data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! This popular Acadia floor plan has been well kept, and it catches your eyes & heart upon entry. It has a Primary suite, 1 Secondary bedroom & 2 full baths downstairs, a study, formal dining, open kitchen, breakfast nook, and its 20ft tall ceilings in living room and foyer makes the space very light & bright. Upstairs has 2 bedrooms, Jack & Jill bath, powder bath off game room with an unfinished 16x16 optional theater room above garage. Smart connected features include an Eero Pro 6 mesh Wi-Fi Chamberlain® Smart Garage hub, Samsung smart hub, Leutron hub, Rucus power over ethernet, energy efficient features 2 Rinnai tankless hot water heaters, R-38 flat ceiling, R-22 slopped ceiling, R-15 walls with blown in insulation, full irrigation system, gutters, NEW ROOF 2021. The community offers a pool, walking trails, 2 catch & release ponds, & HOA covers front yard mowing & pest control. The current loan on this home is assumable. Please reach out to me for more details.
